MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

01-2064. State ex rel. Opre v. Milton Twp. Bd. of Trustees.

In Quo Warranto. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of quo warranto. Upon consideration of relator’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for .dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

*1477ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
